---

<section id="admissions" class="admissions-banner reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="admissions-inner">
      <div class="admissions-text">
        <p class="section-overline" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Admissions 2026–2027</p>
        <h2>Rejoignez le <em>séminaire</em></h2>
        <p>Déposez votre candidature avant le 31 mai 2026. Le séminaire accueille les candidats envoyés par leur évêque et désirant embrasser le ministère ecclésial.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="admissions-cta">
        <a href="/admissions" class="btn btn-dark" style="font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem;">Candidater →</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">Nous contacter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .admissions-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--burgundy) 100%); color: #fff; padding: 5rem 0; }
  .admissions-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 3rem; }
  .admissions-text .section-overline { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .admissions-text h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .admissions-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
  .admissions-text p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width: 500px; }
  .admissions-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .admissions-cta .btn-dark { background: #fff; color: var(--accent); }
  .admissions-cta .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--bg); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .admissions-cta .btn-light { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); color: #fff; }
  .admissions-cta .btn-light:hover { border-color: #fff; color: #fff; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .admissions-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; } .admissions-text p { max-width: 100%; } .admissions-cta { align-items: center; } }
</style>
